<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 13:58:30 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>科学家能否了解到细胞领导的团队旨在解码细胞对话</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/can-scientists-learn-cells-led-team-aims-to-decode-cellular-conversations</link><description>“有许多不同的细胞发挥着不同的作用，”加州大学洛杉矶分校萨穆埃利工程学院的阿蒙德和埃琳娜·海拉佩蒂安教授兼生物工程系主任迪诺·迪·卡洛博士说。 “当这些部分协调一致时——当细胞以正确的方式相互倾听并做出反应时，就会出现健康的组织。” &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/can-scientists-learn-cells-led-team-aims-to-decode-cellular-conversations.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 13:58:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/can-scientists-learn-cells-led-team-aims-to-decode-cellular-conversations</guid></item><item><title>简单语言人工智能工作流程工具可以大幅减少云能源使用和成本</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/plain-language-ai-workflow-tool-could-cut-cloud-energy-use-and-costs-dramatically</link><description>代理工作流程是人工智能驱动的软件系统，它将多个模型和外部工具链接在一起以处理复杂的任务，例如分析视频并回答有关视频的问题。但这些高度分散的系统的设计和部署方式通常会导致效率低下，从而导致计算、能源和成本的浪费。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/plain-language-ai-workflow-tool-could-cut-cloud-energy-use-and-costs-dramatically.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 13:43:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/plain-language-ai-workflow-tool-could-cut-cloud-energy-use-and-costs-dramatically</guid></item><item><title>使用 CRISPR 相关核酸酶 Cas13a 对主要致病性禽白血病病毒亚群进行特异性、灵敏的视觉原病毒 DNA 检测</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/specific-and-sensitive-visual-proviral-dna-detection-of-major-pathogenic-avian-leukosis-virus-subgroups-using-crispr-associated-nuclease-cas13a</link><description>禽白血病病毒（ALV）包括一组主要与家禽肿瘤疾病相关的禽逆转录病毒，通常称为禽白血病。 ALV 亚组 A、B 和 J（ALV-A、ALV-B 和 ALV-J）根据其包膜特性属于不同的亚组，在家禽种群中分布最广。及早识别并从受感染鸡群中清除携带病毒的禽类对于根除 ALV 至关重要。因此，开发快速、准确、简单易用且经济高效的 ALV 亚群现场诊断方法非常重要。 Cas13a 是一种 RNA 引导的 RNA 核酸内切酶，可切割目标单链 RNA，对任何附近的旁观者 RNA 也表现出非特异性核酸内切酶活性。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/specific-and-sensitive-visual-proviral-dna-detection-of-major-pathogenic-avian-leukosis-virus-subgroups-using-crispr-associated-nuclease-cas13a.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 13:28:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/specific-and-sensitive-visual-proviral-dna-detection-of-major-pathogenic-avian-leukosis-virus-subgroups-using-crispr-associated-nuclease-cas13a</guid></item><item><title>通过人工智能评估眼睛微小血管的视频可能会取代针刺进行贫血筛查</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/video-of-tiny-vessels-in-the-eye-assessed-by-ai-may-replace-needle-sticks-for-anemia-screening</link><description>特拉维夫大学和示巴医学中心的一项新合作研究标志着无创血液检测取得了重大进展，这是市场上最重要的未满足需求之一。研究人员开发了一种基于人工智能的系统，能够通过眼睛结膜（覆盖在眼睛白色部分的透明膜）血管的短视频记录来评估血红蛋白水平和红细胞计数，而无需针刺或抽血。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/video-of-tiny-vessels-in-the-eye-assessed-by-ai-may-replace-needle-sticks-for-anemia-screening.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 13:13:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/video-of-tiny-vessels-in-the-eye-assessed-by-ai-may-replace-needle-sticks-for-anemia-screening</guid></item><item><title>CAR T 细胞疗法使 B 细胞淋巴瘤患者获得 10 年缓解</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/car-t-cell-therapy-leads-to-10-year-remissions-in-b-cell-lymphoma-patients</link><description>经过中位 10 年的随访后，超过三分之一的大 B 细胞淋巴瘤患者和近一半的滤泡性淋巴瘤患者接受了单次输注 tisagenlecleucel（由 Carl June 医学博士开发的 CAR T 细胞疗法，该疗法后来成为&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/car-t-cell-therapy-leads-to-10-year-remissions-in-b-cell-lymphoma-patients2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 12:58:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/car-t-cell-therapy-leads-to-10-year-remissions-in-b-cell-lymphoma-patients</guid></item><item><title>治疗前 MRI 作为根治性前列腺切除术后的预后因素：系统回顾和荟萃分析</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/pretreatment-mri-as-a-prognostic-factor-after-radical-prostatectomy-a-systematic-review-and-meta-analysis</link><description>这项系统评价和荟萃分析评估了治疗前磁共振成像 (MRI) 参数对接受根治性前列腺切除术的男性肿瘤学结果的预后价值。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/pretreatment-mri-as-a-prognostic-factor-after-radical-prostatectomy-a-systematic-review-and-meta-analysis2.png" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 12:43:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/pretreatment-mri-as-a-prognostic-factor-after-radical-prostatectomy-a-systematic-review-and-meta-analysis</guid></item><item><title>新型量子计算机的准确性达到了很高的水平——我们是否正处于重大突破的边缘？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/a-new-quantum-computer-sets-a-high-watermark-for-accuracy-are-we-on-the-verge-of-a-big-breakthrough-2</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 12:28:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/a-new-quantum-computer-sets-a-high-watermark-for-accuracy-are-we-on-the-verge-of-a-big-breakthrough-2</guid></item><item><title>脆弱的 ALS 神经元在细胞死亡开始前揭示分子警告信号</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/vulnerable-als-neurons-reveal-molecular-warning-signs-before-cell-death-begins</link><description>Knight Initiative for Brain Resilience 研究人员的一项新研究可能有助于解释肌萎缩侧索硬化症 (ALS) 的一个持久谜团：为什么这种疾病会杀死一些大脑和脊髓的运动控制神经元，而其他神经元则表现出更强的恢复力。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/vulnerable-als-neurons-reveal-molecular-warning-signs-before-cell-death-begins2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 12:13:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/vulnerable-als-neurons-reveal-molecular-warning-signs-before-cell-death-begins</guid></item><item><title>胎盘：在出生前影响人类健康的器官佩里·奥蒂尔尼-吉恩博士</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/the-placenta-the-organ-that-programs-human-health-before-birth-dr-perrie-otierney-ginn</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 11:58:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/the-placenta-the-organ-that-programs-human-health-before-birth-dr-perrie-otierney-ginn</guid></item><item><title>激光束为电子显微镜带来对比</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/laser-beam-brings-contrast-to-electron-microscopy</link><description>物理学家已经展示了一种基于激光的方法，使低温电子显微镜能够比以前更详细地对小蛋白质结构进行成像。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/laser-beam-brings-contrast-to-electron-microscopy2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 11:43:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/laser-beam-brings-contrast-to-electron-microscopy</guid></item></channel></rss>